<page_title>Some common actions in constructing a molecular dynamics model</page_title>
<text> Some common actions in constructing a molecular dynamics model

The tool bar in the following container shows some commonly used actions in MW for constructing a model. When you insert an &quot;Atomistic Simulation&quot; model container, you will probably have a container without a tool bar. To add actions to the tool bar, please pull down the &quot;Action&quot; menu of the container, and choose &quot;Customize&quot;. You will see a dialog window coming up in which you can select an action and insert it to or remove it from the tool bar. After you have done with selecting the actions you need in constructing a model, close the dialog window.
    
 

See the User&apos;s Guide for more information about how to construct a model.

&lt;Index of tips&gt;

</text>
